dc_description_s: This point shapefile represents the extent of Cowcod management and conservation areas in California. These data are based on California Code Title 14, section 150.06. This data set was created to depict the management boundaries for cartographic and illustrative use.
dc_publisher_s: California. Department of Fish and Game. Marine Resources Region
dc_creator_sm: California. Department of Fish and Game. Marine Resources Region
